      "date": "2012-05-22 00:38:31.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/7e160390-a3a1-11e1-b201-52540035b04c).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
